---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="문서">
  <div class="docs-container">
    <h1>문서</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Sudoremove의 AI 교육 자료와 튜토리얼</p>
    
    <div class="notice">
      <p>📚 새로운 문서 사이트가 준비되었습니다!</p>
      <a href="/community/docs/" class="btn btn-primary">새 문서 사이트로 이동</a>
    </div>
    
    <section class="docs-section">
      <h2>Physical AI</h2>
      <div class="docs-grid">
        <a href="/community/docs/physical-ai/getting-started" class="doc-card">
          <h3>Physical AI 개요</h3>
          <p>Physical AI의 기본 개념과 시작 방법</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/community/docs/physical-ai/lerobot" class="doc-card special">
          <h3>🤗 LeRobot 가이드</h3>
          <p>HuggingFace LeRobot 완벽 가이드</p>
          <span class="badge">추천</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="docs-section">
      <h2>LLM 강의 아카이브</h2>
      <div class="docs-grid">
        <a href="/community/docs/llm/basics" class="doc-card">
          <h3>LLM 기초</h3>
          <p>대규모 언어 모델의 기본 개념</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/community/docs/llm/advanced" class="doc-card">
          <h3>고급 주제</h3>
          <p>파인튜닝과 프롬프트 엔지니어링</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* CSS 변수 정의 */
  :root {
    --primary-color: #1a0f1f;
    --secondary-color: #251730;
    --accent-color: #fd7318;
    --text-color: #ffffff;
    --text-muted: #b8b8b8;
  }
  
  /* 배경색 강제 적용 */
  body {
    background: #0d030f !important;
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }
  
  .docs-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .docs-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .docs-section h2 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .docs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .doc-card {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-color);
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  .doc-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.2);
    border-color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .doc-card h3 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .doc-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .doc-card.special {
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
    position: relative;
  }

  .badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: 15px;
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .notice {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .notice p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>